    <!-- Spotlight contents-->
    <!-- Content sections -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important; 
            ">1. Attack on Trump and the 2024 election win</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Donald Trump faced two assassination attempts while campaigning for president in 2024. The first one was in <a href="https://apnews.com/article/trump-assassination-attempt-timeline-59e2f4fcdf8379aa2cb5f141825d60a3" target="_blank">Pennsylvania</a> on July 13, and the other was at his <a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/09/30/politics/ryan-wesley-routh-trump-assassination-attempt-plea/index.html" target="_blank">Florida</a> golf course on September 15. The first attempt fueled online <a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/07/14/nx-s1-5039234/examining-how-narratives-about-the-trump-assassination-attempt-are-resonating" target="_blank">conspiracy theories</a> involving the leftist antifa movement. Trump won the <a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2024-elections/president-results" target="_blank">election</a>, securing all swing states.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <!-- Content sections -->
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="0px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">2. Global election year</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4"> Over <a href="https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2024/12/11/global-elections-in-2024-what-we-learned-in-a-year-of-political-disruption" target="_blank">60 countries</a> held elections in 2024, with many ruling and incumbent parties losing. This marked the third consecutive US presidential election where the incumbent lost. Surveys in 34 countries revealed dissatisfaction with the economy (64%) and democracy (54%). <a href="https://www.voanews.com/a/far-right-support-rose-in-europe-in-2024/7899483.html" target="_blank">Right-wing populism</a> gained ground, especially in European countries like Austria, Belgium, France and Germany, as voters prioritized domestic issues over international challenges. </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="0px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">3. Middle East conflicts</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">The <a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/tag/israel-palestine-conflict/" target="_blank">Israel-Palestine</a> conflict expanded to <a href="https://www.france24.com/en/middle-east/20241229-look-back-2024-retrospective-year-war-upheaval-middle-east-syria-gaza-assad-lebanon" target="_blank">include</a> Lebanon, Yemen, and Iran. Israel directly <a href="https://www.timesofisrael.com/pm-iran-dumbfounded-by-israeli-strikes-saw-investment-in-proxies-go-down-the-drain/" target="_blank">engaged</a> Iran for the first time in decades, killed key leaders of Hamas and Hezbollah, and continued Gaza strikes amid failed ceasefire attempts. The region faces a severe humanitarian crisis, with <a href="https://press.un.org/en/2024/sc15895.doc.htm" target="_blank">famine warnings</a> as humanitarian aid efforts are attacked.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="0px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">4. Assad out</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Bashar al-Assad’s 24-year rule over Syria <a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2024/12/8/what-happened-in-syria-has-al-assad-really-fallen" target="_blank">ended</a> as opposition groups, supported by Turkish factions, took advantage of distractions in Russia and Iran. Syrians celebrate his removal, but the country’s <a href="https://news.un.org/en/story/2024/12/1158311" target="_blank">future is uncertain</a>. Refugees are expected to <a href="https://www.unrefugees.org/news/syria-refugee-crisis-explained/" target="_blank">return</a> as the interim government promises peace and stability.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="0px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">5. 1000 days of Ukraine war</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; filter: blur(5px);">The Russia-Ukraine war has caused <a href="https://www.hrw.org/news/2024/11/19/thousand-days-war-ukraine" target="_blank">significant casualties</a>—43,000 Ukrainian soldiers and 198,000 Russian soldiers killed and a combined 920,000 wounded. While America has supported Ukrainian forces, Russia has made progress and attacked strategic sites, including <a href="https://ukraine.un.org/en/286598-massive-attack-ukraine%E2%80%99s-energy-infrastructure-damages-and-disrupts-essential-services" target="_blank">energy infrastructure</a>. Talks of peace are growing, with Donald Trump expressing interest in mediating. Both Russian and Ukrainian leaders have engaged in preliminary discussions with Trump.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="0px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">6. Severe Weather all over the world</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; filter: blur(5px);">2024 saw record-breaking <a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/gallery/2024/12/24/droughts-floods-wildfires-2024-natural-disasters-in-pictures" target="_blank">natural disasters</a>, including extreme heat, hurricanes, floods, droughts, and wildfires. The global average temperature <a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/12/24/nx-s1-5230783/2024-hottest-year-record-heat-climate-change-el-nino#:~:text=Pop%20Culture-,2024%20was%20the%20hottest%20year%20on%20record.,was%20even%20hotter%20than%20expected." target="_blank">rose 2.7°F</a> above pre-industrial levels. Events like Typhoon Yagi in Southeast Asia, <a href="https://www.britannica.com/event/Hurricane-Helene" target="_blank">Hurricane Helene</a>, <a href="https://www.ecmwf.int/en/about/media-centre/focus/2024/storm-boris-and-european-flooding-september-2024" target="_blank">Storm Boris</a>, <a href="https://www.unicef.org/press-releases/least-90000-children-impacted-cyclone-chido-hits-hard-mozambique" target="_blank">Cyclone Chido</a>, and <a href="https://www.pbs.org/newshour/world/extreme-drought-wildfires-and-deforestation-battered-the-amazon-rainforest-in-2024#:~:text=BOGOTA%2C%20Colombia%20(AP)%20%E2%80%94,year%20for%20fires%20since%202005." target="_blank">Amazon rainforest fires</a> were all linked to climate change.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="0px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">7. The 2024 Paris Olympic and Paralympic games</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; filter: blur(5px);">Paris hosted one of the most <a href="https://olympics.com/ioc/news/paris-2024-record-breaking-olympic-games-on-and-off-the-field" target="_blank">record-breaking</a> Olympic and Paralympic games. It was the first Olympic Games to have its opening ceremony outside the stadium. It was also the first game to reach gender parity and one of the <a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/07/26/economy/olympics-economics-paris-2024/index.html" target="_blank">lowest-cost</a> Olympics in recent history because almost 95% of the infrastructure was already there. The Seine River saw a complete restoration and was put to use for the first time since 1923 after the heavy restoration works. Compared to Rio and London, the <a href="https://olympics.com/ioc/news/paris-2024-record-breaking-olympic-games-on-and-off-the-field" target="_blank">Paris Olympics cut carbon emissions</a> by half.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="0px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">8. Bangladesh ousts PM</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; filter: blur(5px);">A <a href="https://apnews.com/article/bangladesh-sheikh-hasina-prime-minister-fc19afbef9d1c50aaef08648bf37437f" target="_blank">student-led uprising</a> removed Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina. Nobel laureate and founder of Grameen Bank Muhammad Yunus now leads the interim government. Hasina fled to India, which <a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2024/12/23/bangladesh-tells-india-it-wants-ex-pm-hasina-back-for-judicial-process" target="_blank">refused extradition</a>, straining <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/world-news/bangladesh-2024-hasina-flees-to-india-her-dramatic-ouster-casts-shadow-over-dhaka-delhi-ties/articleshow/116672261.cms?from=mdr" target="_blank">diplomatic ties</a>. Efforts are underway to normalize relations as Bangladesh navigates this transition. Attacks on Hindus in Bangladesh continue putting strain on their relationship with India, their biggest trading partner.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="0px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">9. Sudan continues to suffer</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; filter: blur(5px);">Twenty months of <a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/opinions/2024/12/26/sudans-war-came-to-represent-the-worst-of-humanity" target="_blank">fighting</a> between the Rapid Support Forces (RSF) and the Sudanese Army (SAF) have killed at least 20,000 people. Around 25 million people are hungry and in urgent need of help, and over 14 million have been forced to leave their homes. The <a href="https://apnews.com/article/un-sudan-uae-weapons-government-paramilitary-war-859bf38f1a6f6a5647fb528d3818f5bb" target="_blank">UAE</a> and Iran have secretly supplied weapons to both sides, fueling the conflict. Efforts to stop the fighting, led by the African Union, Egypt, and the United States, have failed so far.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
